description: Episode 1: Electrosex yields a unique type of psychological control that I'm not sure Audrey Hollander was prepared for when she signed up for Elelctrosluts. Gia DiMarco, once being on the receiving end of this psychological control knows exactly how to utilize it with this nervous newbie. Gia doesn't hesitate to show Audrey the fun time she can have toying between pain and pleasure. Watch the sentual interaction between Gia and Audrey and Gia warms Audrey up for three more episodes of intense electrosex.
title: Warming up Audrey Hollander
